OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774534302
OL,3,CJury find Meta and YouTube liable in
OL,4,Clandmark social media addiction trial
OL,6,FA jury in the US has found Meta and
OL,7,FYouTube liable on all counts in a
OL,8,Flandmark case that accused the tech
OL,9,Fgiants of intentionally addicting a
OL,10,Fyoung woman and injuring her mental
OL,11,Fhealth.
OL,13,FMeta, which owns Facebook, Instagram
OL,14,Fand Whatsapp, and Google, which owns
OL,15,FYouTube, were negligent in the design
OL,16,Fof their platforms; knew their design
OL,17,Fwas dangerous; failed to warn of those
OL,18,Frisks; and caused substantial harm to
OL,19,Fthe plaintiff, jurors found.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774534302
OL,3,CJury find Meta and YouTube liable in
OL,4,Clandmark social media addiction trial
OL,6,FThe decision could set a precedent for
OL,7,Fhundreds of similar cases and lead to
OL,8,Fmajor changes in how social media
OL,9,Fplatforms operate, especially for
OL,10,Fyoung users, as well as millions, even
OL,11,Fbillions, in losses for the tech
OL,12,Fcompanies.
OL,14,FA now 20-year-old Californian woman
OL,15,Fnamed Kaley and her mother sued Meta,
OL,16,FGoogle's YouTube, Snap and TikTok,
OL,17,Faccusing them of intentionally hooking
OL,18,Fher as a child and causing her to
OL,19,Fdevelop anxiety, body dysmorphia and
OL,20,Fsuicidal thoughts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774534302
OL,3,CJury find Meta and YouTube liable in
OL,4,Clandmark social media addiction trial
OL,6,FSnap and TikTok settled the case
OL,7,Fbefore trial.
OL,9,FThe jury deliberated for more than
OL,10,Feight days after a seven-week trial in
OL,11,FLos Angeles.
OL,13,FThey ordered the companies to pay a
OL,14,Ftotal of $3 million (around
OL,15,F#2,242,950.00) in compensatory damages.
OL,17,FThe jurors will soon deliberate on
OL,18,Fwhether and how much should
OL,19,Fadditionally be awarded in punitive
OL,20,Fdamages, based on the net worth of
OL,21,Feach company.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774534302
OL,3,CJury find Meta and YouTube liable in
OL,4,Clandmark social media addiction trial
OL,6,FMeta bears 70% of the responsibility
OL,7,Ffor Kaley's harms and YouTube 30%,
OL,8,Fjurors found.
OL,10,FKaley was in the courtroom to hear the
OL,11,Fdecision, along with parents of other
OL,12,Fteens who they say were harmed by
OL,13,Fsocial media.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for Meta said the
OL,16,Fcompany would consider its options now.
OL,18,F"We respectfully disagree with the
OL,19,Fverdict and are evaluating our legal
OL,20,Foptions," the spokesperson said.
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774534302
OL,3,CJury find Meta and YouTube liable in
OL,4,Clandmark social media addiction trial
OL,6,FGoogle said they would appeal the
OL,7,Fverdict.
OL,9,F"We disagree with the verdict and plan
OL,10,Fto appeal," Jose Castaneda, a Google
OL,11,Fspokesperson, said in a statement.
OL,13,F"This case misunderstands YouTube,
OL,14,Fwhich is a responsibly built streaming
OL,15,Fplatform, not a social media site."
OL,17,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
