OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774534302
OL,3,CJury find Meta and YouTube liable in
OL,4,Clandmark social media addiction trial
OL,6,FMeta and YouTube had denied the
OL,7,Flawsuit's claims and contested the
OL,8,Fidea that their platform could be
OL,9,Faddictive.
OL,11,FThe tech companies pointed to safety
OL,12,Ffeatures they've rolled out in recent
OL,13,Fyears, such as parental oversight
OL,14,Ftools and teen content and privacy
OL,15,Frestrictions, that they say protect
OL,16,Fteens.
OL,18,FKaley's was the first of more than
OL,19,F1,500 similar cases against the social
OL,20,Fmedia companies to go to trial.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774534302
OL,3,CJury find Meta and YouTube liable in
OL,4,Clandmark social media addiction trial
OL,6,FThe trial's outcome won't determine -
OL,7,Fbut could help guide - how those other
OL,8,Fcases are resolved.
OL,10,FRepeated losses could put the tech
OL,11,Fgiants on the hook for up to billions
OL,12,Fof dollars and force them to change
OL,13,Ftheir platforms, online safety experts
OL,14,Fwarned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774534302
OL,3,CJury find Meta and YouTube liable in
OL,4,Clandmark social media addiction trial
OL,6,F"Social media giants would never have
OL,7,Ffaced trial if they had prioritised
OL,8,Fkids' safety over engagement," James
OL,9,FSteyer, founder and CEO of online
OL,10,Fsafety watchdog Common Sense Media,
OL,11,Fsaid in a statement following the Los
OL,12,FAngeles decision.
OL,14,F"Instead, they buried their own
OL,15,Fresearch showing children were being
OL,16,Fharmed, and used kids and society as
OL,17,Fguinea pigs in massive, uncontrolled,
OL,18,Fand wildly profitable experiments.
OL,19,FNow, executives are being held to
OL,20,Faccount."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@^O]vD@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774534302
OL,3,CJury find Meta and YouTube liable in
OL,4,Clandmark social media addiction trial
OL,6,FKaley, who was referred to by only her
OL,7,Ffirst name because her claims relate
OL,8,Fto incidents that took place while she
OL,9,Fwas a minor, described in court how
OL,10,Fher addiction continues to disrupt her
OL,11,Fadult life, making her feel compelled
OL,12,Fto sneak out of work to scroll and
OL,13,Fspend long hours trying to manipulate
OL,14,Fher appearance using filters on the
OL,15,Fapps.
OL,17,FMeta had claimed that it was Kaley's
OL,18,Fdifficult childhood, not social media,
OL,19,Fthat caused her mental health
OL,20,Fchallenges.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774534302
OL,3,CJury find Meta and YouTube liable in
OL,4,Clandmark social media addiction trial
OL,6,FKaley's lawyer, Mark Lanier, argued
OL,7,Fthat those challenges simply raised
OL,8,Fthe stakes for the companies to
OL,9,Fprotect children.
OL,11,FYouTube had said that records from
OL,12,FKaley's account showed she used the
OL,13,Fplatform for only a short time each
OL,14,Fday, which they said contradicted her
OL,15,Fclaims of addiction.
OL,17,FBut Lanier said that, like many kids,
OL,18,FKaley often used the platform while
OL,19,Fnot logged into her account.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774534302
OL,3,CJury find Meta and YouTube liable in
OL,4,Clandmark social media addiction trial
OL,6,FThe trial saw testimony from top
OL,7,Fexecutives at the companies, including
OL,8,FMeta CEO Mark Zuckerberg, Instagram's
OL,9,Fhead Adam Mosseri, and YouTube Vice
OL,10,FPresident of Engineering Cristos
OL,11,FGoodrow.
OL,13,FMosseri testified that he believes
OL,14,Fsocial media use can be "problematic"
OL,15,Fbut not "clinically addictive."
OL,17,FGoodrow testified that his own
OL,18,Fchildren use YouTube for hours each
OL,19,Fday and he believes it's "good" for
OL,20,Fthem.
OL,26,@vD@YOUvD@eO]wD@IOUwD@_O]{D@ZOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774534302
OL,3,CJury find Meta and YouTube liable in
OL,4,Clandmark social media addiction trial
OL,6,FInternal documents presented in court
OL,7,Fshed light on the companies' efforts
OL,8,Fto attract young users, as well as
OL,9,Fwhat they knew about the potential
OL,10,Frisks to their platforms.
OL,12,FMeta documents, for example, showed
OL,13,Fhow the company decided to allow
OL,14,F"beauty" filters that manipulate a
OL,15,Fuser's appearance despite employees
OL,16,Fand 18 experts raising concerns that
OL,17,Fthey could be harmful.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
